                    Creating Minecraft plugins gave me an entry point into the field of Java programming from which I learned
                    various skills.
                ul.lead
                    li Utilizing the Java programming language to create OOP software for Spigot servers
                    li Utilizing Git as an SCM to effectively manage source code
                    li Utilizing Maven and Gradle as build systems to manage dependencies and create JARs
                    li Utilizing SQL databases to enable cloud data persistence
                    li Utilizing a combination of technologies including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and PHP to design and develop websites
            .col-sm-12.col-lg-4
